Package org.bonitasoft.engine.page

Interface Page

All Superinterfaces:
BaseElement, BonitaObject, Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
PageImpl
public interface Page extends BaseElement
A Page is a way to store, amongst other things, a binary content. It is used by Bonita Portal to display specific custom content
Author:
Laurent Leseigneur
